  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK581">
<l>oṟṟu muraicāṉṟa nūlu mivaiyiraṇṭun </l>
<l> teṟṟeṉka maṉṉavaṉ kaṇ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Let a king consider as his eyes these two things, a spy and a book (of laws) universally esteemed.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
